nodes.text: I have tons of pics of my 'wedding' in September and I look like a dork in everyone one of them. Every single shot, I have some dumb goofy expression on my face..... I have deep sympathy for anyone who has to look at pics of their own ceremony if they hate the pics of themself
I know what you mean, my Girlfriend says I always put on a goofy grin every time I get my photo take or if I don't do that I seem to close my eyes just as the picture is taken.
OHHHHH I do send me please :) :) I love to see men in kilts the hairier the better :)
